        void assertResponse​(int statusCode,
                    java.lang.String entity,
                    java.lang.String... headerNameValuePairs)
        Asserts the contents of the HttpResponse.
        Parameters:
        statusCode - Expected status code.
        entity - Expected entity.
        headerNameValuePairs - Expected HttpHeader name/value pairs. This only confirms they exist on the HttpResponse. It is not inclusive to check if these are the only HttpHeader instances.
